//canada.forever21.com ( collectively , the " Websites " ) , and to our fashion marketing and sales activities , including sales through our store locations , in the United States and Canada under our brands Forever 21 , Heritage 1981 , Twelve by Twelve , Reference , For Love 21 and Gadzooks .
This Privacy Policy protects consumers providing information through our Websites and stores and is not designed to protect business information .
