If your account information is incomplete , inaccurate or not current , please follow the instructions for My Account on our Websites to correct or update your account information online , or you may contact Customer Service at www.forever21.com/customerservice or call in the U.S. or Canada 1-888-494-3837 ( EVER ) ( - Toll Free ) .
If you need additional assistance or wish more information about our privacy practices , please call in the U.S. or Canada 1-888-494-3837 ( EVER ) ( - Toll Free ) and ask to speak to our Privacy Officer .
