In addition , such data may be stored on servers located in the United States , which may have less stringent privacy practices than those your own resident jurisdiction .
By providing us with your data , you consent to transfer of such data .
If Forever 21 should ever file for bankruptcy or merge with another company , or if Forever 21 should decide to buy another business , or sell or reorganize part or all of Forever 21 's business , Forever 21 may be required to disclose your personal information to prospective or actual purchasers and other parties .
